Project cleanup requirements

1) Stop local app/runtime services:
- Flutter and Dart processes
- Android emulator (via adb)
- Node/Python background services in this project

2) Remove disposable local artifacts inside Lesson18:
- node_modules
- venv / .venv
- .pytest_cache
- *.pyc
- istio-related files/directories (name contains "istio")

3) Stop Docker containers and remove unused Docker resources:
- stop running containers
- docker system prune -af --volumes

4) Keep repository clean:
- ensure .gitignore includes common cache/build/runtime artifacts
- document stop/cleanup commands in README

